00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.820
So as a little bit of a fun exercise,

00:00:15.820 --> 00:00:19.735
I'll like to challenge you to draw a Mickey Mouse's face.

00:00:19.735 --> 00:00:21.670
Now it doesn't need to be perfect,

00:00:21.670 --> 00:00:25.465
the whole idea is just to give you something to practice with,

00:00:25.465 --> 00:00:30.305
which involves some of the techniques which we looked at throughout this course and

00:00:30.305 --> 00:00:32.200
it also gives you a chance to think about things

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:35.195
yourself rather than typing along with me.

00:00:35.195 --> 00:00:39.340
So this is what I come up with and this is what I'd like you to create.

00:00:39.340 --> 00:00:45.590
